      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FIGHT FOR VICTORY (7) has had two runs this campaign and is yet to finish in the top three. Was again unable to find the frame last time when he finished fourth over 2138m at this track, beaten 3.5 metres. Has to contend with a very wide draw. Good enough to put himself in the winners' stall. SCHOONERS (3) is an in-form filly who has managed two wins and two minor placings from four starts this time in work. Produced another fine effort last start when she finished second over 1780m at Redcliffe, beaten 3.5 metres. Has the benefit of a good draw. Meets a similar line up and she is a strong winning hope. LOSTANDFOUND (1) has bene racing well and should get the favours from this draw. BETTOR BE BODHI (5) cannot be left out after solid recent performances, the latest a sound third at this track over 2138m.",
